<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>prabhava saṁvvatsara Āsvija ba 6 ma 
<lb n="2" break="no"/>śrī malikagaja siṁvvarāvu jā 
<lb n="3" break="no"/>svivula tippanāyaniṁgāri kārya 
<lb n="4" break="no"/>karttalaina siṁggāpaṁḍḍitulu pulipā 
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ṭi Ānumaṁttuni sāṣṭāṁgga daṁ 
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ṇaṁveṭi yiccina dharmmaśā 
<lb n="7" break="no"/>sanaṁ ssamiki Amṛtapaḷla 
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ku yiccina kṣētraṁ grāmāna 
<lb n="9" break="no"/>ku tūrpū rēgaḍi gaḍaṁnāgi cēnista 
<lb n="10" break="no"/>laṁ kuccalaku na 2 sīmayeli ve 
<lb n="11" break="no"/>ligōṭi rāyapaneniṁgārki pu 
<lb n="12" break="no"/>ṇyamuṁgānuṁnnu tiṁppanāya 
<lb n="13" break="no"/>nigāri puṇyamugānuṁnnu sa 
<lb n="14" break="no"/>marppistimi yiṁdku tappi 
<lb n="15" break="no"/>navāru gā<unclear>r</unclear>ddabhamuku puṭina 
<lb n="16" break="no"/>vāṁḍu 
</p>

